fields.name: NIKE MENS DRY YOGA VEST
fields.description: Made from soft, sweat-wicking fabric, the Nike Dri-FIT Tank helps keep you dry and focused through your routine. Wide armholes and hem vents at the hem let you move smoothly from one pose to the next. Soft fabric with Dri-FIT technology helps you stay dry and comfortable. Hem vents let you move naturally through your routine. A centre seam on the front helps with alignment as you position yourself. Hem is slightly longer in the back to help keep you covered while you bend and stretch.

fields.name: Dare 2b - Men's Righteous Long Sleeved Graphic Tee
fields.description: The Righteous Long Sleeved Tee. Made from moisture-wicking, soft-to-wear Q-Wic fabric. Lightweight, quick-drying and made from 88% Polyester. Featuring reflective trim. For cycling, running and everything in between.

fields.name: Nike Swim Men's Essential Lap 5
fields.description: Volley Short has a durable water repellent finish to speed up the drying process when you're ready to head out for lunch. A built-in mesh brief and mesh pockets add valuable extra support and storage space to the swimming trunks. The sleek men's swim trunks have a secure elastic waist with a drawcord, so you can count on them to stay in place through each lap.

fields.name: adidas Mens TIRO21 Pant Navy
fields.description: Adidas Tiro 21 Training Pants were born from football culture. They'll keep you comfortable with moisture- absorbing AEROREADY. The classic Tiro tapered legs and ankle zips let you put your footwear on display. This product is made with Primegreen, a series of high- performance recycled materials.

fields.name: adidas Mens STANFRD Pant Navy
fields.description: Thanks to a cosy feel and moisture-absorbing AEROREADY, these adidas casual pants will quickly become favourites. They're made for layering, with an elastic waist and ankle zips so you can slide them on and off without taking off your shoes. This product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials.

fields.name: NIKE MENS DF ACDPR PANT KPZ BLACK
fields.description: SWEAT-WICKING COMFORT. The Nike Dri-FIT Academy Pro Pants feature sweat-wicking fabric to help keep you dry and moving fast on the field. This product is made with at least 75% recycled polyester fibers.

fields.name: PUMA MENS TRAINING PWRFLEECE HOODIE GREEN
fields.description: The Train PWRFLEECE Hoodie is perfect for the guy that wants to stand out. This hoodie features PUMA’s PWRFLEECE, storage solutions, ergonomic cut lines, a bold PUMA taping around the hood and PUMA’s signature warmCELL technology.

fields.name: adidas Mens 3S FL Hoodie Orange
fields.description: Upgrade your everyday hoodie. This adidas hoodie's look is inspired by the timeless style of vintage post-workout gear. It's cut from soft fleece fabric and has a classic fit that you know and love. Ribbing at the cuffs and hem ensures a sleek look that's never slouchy. This product is made with recycled content as part of adidas’ ambition to end plastic waste. adidas' cotton products support sustainable cotton farming.

fields.name: UNDER ARMOUR MENS RUSH FULLZIP HOODIE BLACK
fields.description: Under Armour RUSH is the gear you wear when it matters most—your toughest workouts, your biggest games, your most intense training. It fits great, keeps you dry, and makes you feel like you can crush every PR.

fields.name: ADIDAS MENS SUPERNOVA
fields.description: Your run starts before your feet even hit the pavement. With a spark, a goal or a desire to be your best self. Lace into these adidas running shoes and the run starts now. High-performance elements like responsive cushioning and supportive overlays keep you cruising in comfort. The breathable, seamless upper means cool feet even when you ramp up the speed.

fields.name: UNDER ARMOUR MENS CHARGED ROGUE 2.5
fields.description: Quick jog today, long run tomorrow. The UA Charged Rogue excels at everything. Get better shock-absorption and the support of a locked-in heel to help you go as far as you want, or farther. Engineered mesh upper is extremely lightweight and breathable, with strategic support where you need it. Lightweight, external heel counter for additional support that keeps the back of the foot locked in place. Dual midsole combines Micro G® with Charged Cushioning® for the ultimate blend of comfort and energy return. Removable, comfort sockliner provides a comfortable and responsive ride. Solid rubber outsole covers high impact zones for greater durability with less weight.

fields.name: UNDER ARMOUR MENS HOVR MACHINA 2
fields.description: UA HOVR™ Machina 2 is more than a running shoe. Yes, it gives you energy return and the speed of a Pebax® propulsion plate, but it also coaches you in real-time to help you run better when you connect them to UA MapMyRun™. UA HOVR™ technology provides 'zero gravity feel' to maintain energy return that helps eliminate impact. Compression mesh Energy Web contains and moulds UA HOVR™ foam to give back the energy you put in. Ultralight 3D spacer mesh upper for increased breathability and ultimate speed. As your body emits energy, the mineral-infused UA RUSH™ lining absorbs and reflects it back, improving endurance. External heel counter for added stability and a locked-in feel. Sprint spike-inspired Pebax® speed plate for increased return and more powerful push-offs. Carbon rubber pods under the heel deliver greater traction and durability at high-impact strike zones.

fields.name: UNDER ARMOUR MENS TRIBASE REIGN 3
fields.description: Every lift, rep, and WOD starts from the ground up. UA TriBase™ tech maximises your floor contact with a low, stable, triangular base that lets your foot flex naturally. Engineered mesh upper with knit bootie construction and overlays for added durability and abrasion-resistance. External heel counter for added stability with ridge construction for traction during headstand pushups. Engineered zonal flex and traction in the forefoot allows for greater mobility and added grip. Full-length Micro G® foam midsole for the ultimate in responsive cushioning. UA TriBase™ maximizes ground contact, promotes natural motion and provides flexibility to grip during lifts. Full-rubber outsole wraps up the sides for durability and added abrasion resistance with medial rope grip. Strategic rubber build under the toe box for a more powerful floor grip. Low to the ground construction allows for greater feel and power transfer.

fields.name: Nike SuperRep Go 2
fields.description: The Nike SuperRep Go 2 combines lightweight cushioning underfoot and breathable mesh up top to get you moving comfortably in circuit-based fitness classes or while streaming workouts at home. With the supportive arc on the side and extra flexibility in the sole, you're ready to go for 1 more rep. Colour Shown: Dark Smoke Grey/Clear Emerald/White/Total Orange

fields.name: Nike Metcon 7 X
fields.description: The Nike Metcon 7 X is the gold standard for weight training—even tougher and more stable than previous versions. We've also added React foam that ups the comfort to keep you ready for high-intensity cardio. Plus, a tab locks down your laces so you can forget about them coming untied when you're focused on your next PR. Colour Shown: Pollen/Volt/Pale Coral/Black

fields.name: ASICS GT-1000 10 MENS RUNNING SHOES
fields.description: The 10th anniversary of the GT-1000™ running shoe takes a big step forward in what this model stands for. Designed for the runner with an active lifestyle, they're seeking a lightweight everyday trainer with excellent cushioning. The upper has been reimagined with a new engineered mesh that adjusts to your foot's natural shape while providing a comfortable midfoot hold. With the addition of an integrated support system, this application improves the heel fit and creates a more secure feel. Following a more sustainable design approach, this shoe also uses fewer resources to colour the sockliner. Featuring a layer of GEL™ technology cushioning in the heel to improve shock absorption, the shoe also integrates a FLYTEFOAM™ midsole material that offers a softer and more supportive feeling at footstrike. Lastly, the DUOMAX™ support system consists of a firmer density of foam placed on the medial side of the midsole to help reduce the foot's pronounced inward roll (overpronation) while improving stability.

fields.name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 A.I.R.Nathan Bell
fields.description: Your workhorse with wings returns with hand-drawn sketches by Nathan Bell—celebrating the run as a competition with yourself.This breathable version has a wider fit at the toes and plenty of cushioned support to help you fly past your personal goals. Colour Shown: Aluminium/Sail/Black/Game Royal

fields.name: Nike MD Runner 2
fields.description: Nod to the running champ from the '90s.The Nike MD Runner 2 keeps the OG details in place with breathable mesh and soft leather details.Its low-top design adds a heritage Waffle sole and foam cushioning for comfort. Colour Shown: Black/Anthracite/White

fields.name: Nike Revolution 5 FlyEase
fields.description: Designed with a zip closure secured by a midfoot strap, the Nike Revolution 5 FlyEase lets you suit up for your run quickly and easily. Soft foam cushions your stride, while a minimalist design fits in just about anywhere. Colour Shown: Black/Anthracite/White

fields.name: Nike Downshifter 11
fields.description: The Nike Downshifter 11 gives you lightweight, flexible support to keep you going. It continues the same soft cushioning from the last version, and adds more support around the midfoot, to make it comfortable to wear long after your workout. Colour Shown: Platinum Tint/Wolf Grey/Chile Red/Summit White

fields.name: Nike Revolution 5 EXT
fields.description: The Nike Revolution 5 EXT delivers a premium spin on a favourite.It cushions your stride with soft foam to keep you running in comfort.Lightweight mesh material wraps your foot in breathable support, while a minimalist design fits in just about anywhere your day takes you. Colour Shown: Black/Dark Smoke Grey/White/Coast
